# Allowlist: the API image (apps/api/Dockerfile, context = repo root) copies
# only the paths re-included below. Everything else stays out of the context.
*
!README.md
!pyproject.toml
!apps/api/src
!apps/api/tests
!scripts/testing

# Caches inside the re-included trees
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.egg-info
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
